use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ldy1665702565599.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ldy1665702565599.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ldy1665702565599.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ldy1665702565599\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $newstruct\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ldy1665702565599___newstruct_275366\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Explicitly create a new Struct with no members.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__topic_d86213e1_d86214e1_d86215e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__p_d86216e1_d86217e1_d86218e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">StructVar</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$newstruct</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__section_w2465ab1b7b5_w2466ab1b7_w2467ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__p_d86219e1_d86220e1_d86221e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vStruct1-&gt;mbr = $newstruct</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__topic_d57332e1_d57333e1_d57334e1_d57335e1_d57336e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d520761e81\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__table_d9116e1_d9117e1_d9118e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__table_d9116e1_d9117e1_d9118e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__table_d9116e1_d9117e1_d9118e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__table_d9116e1_d9117e1_d9118e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ldy1665702565599__table_d9116e1_d9117e1_d9118e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">StructVar</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ldy1665702565599__table_d9116e1_d9117e1_d9118e1__entry__2\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">struct</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ldy1665702565599__table_d9116e1_d9117e1_d9118e1__entry__3\">Name of a variable or parameter; must be of\n                        type <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">struct</span> or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">any</span>. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__topic_d57337e1_d57338e1_d57339e1_d57340e1_d57341e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d520761e144\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__p_d86228e1_d86229e1_d86230e1\">Returns an empty Struct.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__topic_d57342e1_d57343e1_d57344e1_d57345e1_d57346e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d520761e154\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__topic_d57347e1_d57348e1_d57349e1_d57350e1_d57351e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d520761e163\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__p_d86240e1_d86241e1_d86242e1\">Structs are usually implicitly created by assigning a value to a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">struct</span> variable or parameter. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$newstruct</span> function enables you to explicitly create an empty Struct or Struct member, which you can then populate.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__section_u2w_mhf_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d520761e178\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$newstruct</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following statement inserts a reference to an empty Struct\n               (referenced by <code class=\"ph codeph\">vStruct1</code>) called <code class=\"ph codeph\">mbr</code>. </p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__pre_wmj_nhf_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vStruct1-&gt;mbr = $newstruct </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The following statement would rarely be required except, for example,\n               if it were used in a loop that needs to reinitialize <code class=\"ph codeph\">vStruct2</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ldy1665702565599__pre_xmj_nhf_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vStruct2 = $newstruct</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529523\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529523\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$newstruct Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $newstruct Explicitly create a new Struct with no members. StructVar = $newstruct Example: vStruct1->mbr = $newstruct Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description StructVar struct Name of a variable or parameter; must be of type struct or any . Return Values Returns an empty Struct. Use Allowed in all component types. Description Structs are usually implicitly created by assigning a value to a struct variable or parameter. The $newstruct function enables you to explicitly create an empty Struct or Struct member, which you can then populate. Example: Using $newstruct The following statement inserts a reference to an empty Struct (referenced by vStruct1 ) called mbr . vStruct1->mbr = $newstruct Copy The following statement would rarely be required except, for example, if it were used in a loop that needs to reinitialize vStruct2 . vStruct2 = $newstruct Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}